OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry at first
OL,6,Fwith some brightness, but increasingly
OL,7,Fcloudy through the evening and
OL,8,Fovernight. Mostly dry but some light
OL,9,Fdrizzle in places, then perhaps the
OL,10,Fodd heavy shower developing in the
OL,11,Feast later.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FAny heavier showers soon
OL,14,Fclearing east in the morning.
OL,15,FOtherwise cooler, dull and cloudy with
OL,16,Fsome patchy light drizzle possible.
OL,17,FBrightening up in the west in the
OL,18,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
